## TECH STACK BY TIER

PULSE TIER — Web dashboard:
- React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
- Tailwind CSS v3 pinned — NEVER v4
- localStorage ONLY — no exceptions
- No server. No API. No cloud DB.
- No Supabase. No Vercel functions.
- No OpenAI. No Anthropic.
- Deploys to Netlify on push to main

VAULT TIER — Desktop app:
- Tauri v2 + React 19 + TypeScript + Vite 5
- Tailwind CSS v3 pinned — NEVER v4
- SQLite via tauri-plugin-sql
- Ollama via invoke() — NEVER fetch()
- Fully airgapped — nothing leaves machine
- No cloud DB. No hosted anything.

## STZ BUILD SEQUENCE

Before writing any code:
1. Run all 25 STZ SME Interview questions
2. Fill prompts/ from L1 answers
3. Fill skills/ from L2 answers
4. Fill agents/ from L3 answers
5. Fill contracts/ from L4 answers
6. Fill evaluation/ from L5 answers
7. Then and only then — start building

STZ layers are build methodology.
Product tiers are commercial packaging.
Never confuse them.

## BRAND COLORS — ALL CLIENT BUILDS

Navy:   #2D4459  sidebar, headings
Teal:   #3BBFBF  primary action, active states
Mint:   #C8E8E5  borders, backgrounds, badges
Coral:  #F05F57  critical alerts, danger
Gold:   #C8974A  warnings, attention
Slate:  #7A8F95  muted text, labels
Cream:  #FEFAF6  page backgrounds
Green:  #3A7D5C  success states
White:  #FFFFFF  cards, panels

## FIVE PULSE PAGES — EVERY DEPLOYMENT

Every client deployment includes exactly
these five pages configured for their vertical:

1. Morning Brief — what needs attention today
2. Business Goals — revenue target tracking
3. Client Intelligence — every client organized
4. Health Interventions — signals and responses
5. My Practice — patterns learned over time

## WRITING RULES

- NO em dashes ever
- NO generic AI language
- Every acronym explained on first use
- Every output sounds like the client expert
- Not like a template — not like generic AI
- Glass box always — auditable outputs only

## PROMPT DISCIPLINE

One fix per prompt.
One file per prompt.
Always end with: npx tsc --noEmit
Always git add specific files only.
NEVER git add .
Report commit hash only.

## GOVERNANCE — NON-NEGOTIABLE

Every action logged to audit_log.
Human approval on every output.
Nothing leaves machine without review.
HIPAA compliance for healthcare verticals.
EU AI Act for high-risk verticals.
PII never in cloud systems.
Airgapped is the brand. Not a feature.

## WHAT NEVER TO DO

- NEVER use em dashes
- NEVER build from scratch — always clone
- NEVER put client files in this repo
- NEVER use Electron
- NEVER upgrade Tailwind to v4
- NEVER use integer IDs
- NEVER use OpenAI or Anthropic API in products
- NEVER store client data in cloud
- NEVER send output without human approval
- NEVER git add . — always specific files
